data.text:
Kanye has made several announcements about new music due out from G.O.O.D. Music this year, including a collaborative album with Kid Cudi, and new albums from Teyana Taylor and Pusha T. Now, the Chicago-born rapper has announced that he’s also producing a new Nas album that’s due out on June 15.

He tweeted, “I’m hand producing all the albums I tweeted about. Been chopping samples from the sunken place Pusha May 25th My album June 1st me and Cudi June 8th and Teyana June 22nd and oh yeah…Nas June 15th.”
